SELECT m.id, 'Introduction', 'introduction', '<p>Click the link below to download our Desiccant Dehumidification Training Manual.</p>
<p><a href="#">D3_Training_Manual_rev7.2025.pdf</a></p>
<p>Solid desiccant dehumidifiers are utilized in removing humidity from the air to create and sustain comfortable, healthy, and productive indoor environments.</p>
<p>Most desiccant dehumidifiers function primarily the same way: they remove water from the air in its molecular state, using the vapor pressure differential between the air and the desiccant surface to attract and hold, or oppositely release that moisture.</p>
<p>Perhaps in the past you have been led to believe that solid desiccant dehumidification is too complex and confusing to understand. Or maybe you thought that solid desiccant dehumidification is inefficient, overly expensive, and should only be applied in extreme cases where it must be used. We hope the information we share in the following pages will put these misconceptions to rest. As you read, you will see that solid desiccant dehumidification is an energy-efficient, sustainable, and cost-effective solution for almost any environment, making it a thermodynamically-elegant dehumidification option when properly applied.</p>
<h3>In this course, you will learn:</h3>
<ol>
<li>The process of air flow in a desiccant dehumidification system</li>
<li>What a desiccant is and how it works</li>
<li>The difference between desiccant dehumidification and traditional refrigerant-based dehumidification</li>
<li>The difference between the process and reactivation air streams</li>
<li>What a rotor is</li>
<li>The components of a desiccant dehumidifier</li>
<li>How desiccant dehumidification is sustainable and energy efficient</li>
<li>Factors that affect dehumidification loads and calculations</li>
<li>Available options and add-ons for Innovative Air Technologies desiccant dehumidifiers</li>
<li>Common applications for desiccant dehumidification</li>
</ol>
<figure class="img-missing"><figcaption>📷 Image from Trainual: Solid desiccant dehumidifier unit exterior view — re-upload via admin editor</figcaption></figure>', 0, TRUE, 3
FROM learn_modules m JOIN learn_categories c ON c.id = m.category_id
WHERE c.slug = 'technical-training' AND m.slug = 'dessicant-dehumidification-training'
ON CONFLICT (module_id, slug) DO NOTHING;
